<template><div><h1 id="字符串方法" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#字符串方法" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 字符串方法</h1>
<h2 id="includes-方法" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#includes-方法" aria-hidden="true">#</a> includes() 方法</h2>
<p><strong>介绍：</strong> 查找字符串，如果在<em>string 中</em>找到<em>子字符串</em>，<strong>includes()</strong> 方法返回<em>true</em>。否则，它返回 <strong>false</strong>。</p>
<p><strong>使用</strong></p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="shiki one-dark-pro" style="background-color: #282c34" tabindex="0"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #7F848E; font-style: italic">/** 数组中使用 */</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #C678DD">let</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF"> </span><span style="color: #E06C75">arr</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF"> </span><span style="color: #56B6C2">=</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF"> [</span><span style="color: #98C379">&#39;小明&#39;</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">, </span><span style="color: #98C379">&#39;小杨&#39;</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">];</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #E5C07B">arr</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">.</span><span style="color: #61AFEF">includes</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">(</span><span style="color: #98C379">&quot;小明&quot;</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">);  </span><span style="color: #7F848E; font-style: italic">// 返回 true</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #E5C07B">arr</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">.</span><span style="color: #61AFEF">includes</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">(</span><span style="color: #98C379">&quot;明&quot;</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">);  </span><span style="color: #7F848E; font-style: italic">// 返回 false</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #7F848E; font-style: italic">/** 字符串中使用 */</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #C678DD">let</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF"> </span><span style="color: #E06C75">arr</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF"> </span><span style="color: #56B6C2">=</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF"> [</span><span style="color: #98C379">&#39;小明&#39;</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">, </span><span style="color: #98C379">&#39;小杨&#39;</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">];</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #E5C07B">arr</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">.</span><span style="color: #61AFEF">includes</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">(</span><span style="color: #98C379">&quot;小明&quot;</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">);  </span><span style="color: #7F848E; font-style: italic">// 返回 true</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #E5C07B">arr</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">.</span><span style="color: #61AFEF">includes</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">(</span><span style="color: #98C379">&quot;明&quot;</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">);  </span><span style="color: #7F848E; font-style: italic">// 返回 false</span></span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div></div></template>


